%% CI/CD -- recommended staged pipeline (not confirmed as an existing implemented workflow)
%% Referenced in: docs/deployment.md
flowchart LR
    Commit[Commit / PR] --> Lint[Lint<br/>catch style/type issues cheaply]
    Lint --> Test[Unit Test<br/>flutter test / gradlew test]
    Test --> Build[Build<br/>produce deployable artifact]
    Build --> Staging[Deploy to Staging]
    Staging --> Smoke[Smoke Test<br/>confirm it responds before routing real traffic]
    Smoke --> Prod[Deploy to Production<br/>blue-green / canary, once backend is stateless]

    Smoke -->|fails| Rollback[Block promotion]
